Class BlockMasterWorkerServiceHandler

  • java.lang.Object

    public class BlockMasterWorkerServiceHandler
extends Object
implements BlockMasterWorkerService.Iface
    This class is a Thrift handler for block master RPCs invoked by a Tachyon worker.
